  ANALYSIS:

  beta_y | y1 ON s;
  delta_y | y20 ON s;
  beta_s | s ON y20&1;
  ar_s | s ON s&1;
  s (resvar_s);

  %BETWEEN%
  mu BY y1-y20@1;
  mu;
  [mu];
  [y1-y20@0];
  y1-y20@0;

  day_ar by day_ar1-day_ar19@1;
  day_ar*0.01;
  [day_ar*0.6];
  [day_ar1-day_ar19@0];
  day_ar1-day_ar19@0;

  [beta_y](a);
  [beta_s](b);

  mu day_ar night_ar-ar_s s WITH
     mu day_ar night_ar-ar_s s;

  MODEL CONSTRAINT:
  NEW(indirect);
  indirect = a * b;

  OUTPUT:
  TECH1 TECH8 STDYX FSCOMPARISON STAND(CLUSTER);

  PLOT:
  TYPE = PLOT3;
  FACTOR = ALL (500);

  SAVEDATA:
  FILE IS na_sleep_step2.dat;
  SAVE IS FSCORES (500);
